#: ../../source/soft_connection.rst:2
msgid "Soft Connection"
msgstr "软连接"

#: ../../source/soft_connection.rst:4
msgid ""
"Soft connection is a spring, which constraint two rigidbody. But soft "
"connection only constraint location. Often used for lateral constraints "
"on skirts or cloaks to prevent excessive mesh deformation. If you wan to "
"make the floating widget, set the joint instead, because soft connection "
"can not constraint angle."
msgstr ""
"软连接是一个弹簧，约束两个刚体。 但软连接仅约束位置。 通常用于裙子或斗篷"
"上的横向约束，以防止网格过度变形。 如果你想制作浮动部件，请设置关节，因为"
"软连接不能约束角度。"

#: ../../source/soft_connection.rst:6
msgid ""
"In rigidbody modify mode, you can press Ctrl+W to add soft connection in "
"batch(skirt using \"tube\" option, cope using \"plane\" option, create "
"single soft connection using \"pair\" option)"
msgstr ""
"在刚体修改模式下，可以按Ctrl+W批量添加软连接（裙边使用“tube”选项，coe使"
"用“plane”选项，创建单个软连接使用“pair”选项）"
